mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "Feature Fashion", "As I See It", "Discovery: Dept. for New Square Dancers", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Interview: Bruce Johnson", "So-You Want To Start A Square Dance Business", "Homes For Square Dancing: Prairie Hall, Eugene, Oregon", "Lift and Use", "Style Series: Red Hot", "16th Nat'l Square Dance Convention", "Round the Outside Ring", "SIO Workshop", "The Caller of the Month: Vic Harris", "Paging the Roundancers: Circling the Years" and "Experimental Lab: Slip, Slide & Swing".
